<article>
    <h1>Get&#xAD;ting smarter by the day</h1>
    <h2></h2>
    <section>
        <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/textview" title="The Straits Times">The Straits Times</a>
        - <a href="/singapore/the-straits-times/20201109/textview" title="The Straits Times - 2020-11-09"><time>2020-11-09</time></a>
        - <span>PLACE</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>China Con­struc­tion (South Pa­cific) Devel­op­ment Co has lever­aged dig­i­tal tools to com­plete projects suc­cess­fully</p>
    <p>By em­brac­ing tech­nol­ogy, the com­pany has made sig­nif­i­cant break­throughs in both busi­ness pro­duc­tiv­ity and WSH per­for­mance, says its se­nior man­ager of QEHS (Qual­ity, En­vi­ron­men­tal, Oc­cu­pa­tional Health & Safety) Kwek Hai Chuan.</p>
    <p>Smart dig­i­tal so­lu­tions for WSH that have been in­cor­po­rated in­clude ar­ti­fi­cial in­tel­li­gence (AI) ca­pa­bil­ity-build­ing through CCTVs and Un­manned Aerial Ve­hi­cles, and the expansion of WSH mod­ules in a Com­mon Data En­vi­ron­ment with dash­boards for an­a­lyt­ics that are ex­tended to su­per­vi­sors, en­gi­neers, safety per­son­nel and the per­son­nel at man­age­ment level.</p>
    <p>This is on top of adopt­ing more De­sign for Man­u­fac­tur­ing and Assem­bly (DfMA) al­ter­na­tives such as Pre­fab­ri­cated Bath­room Units (PBU) and Pre­fab­ri­cated Pre­fin­ished Vol­u­met­ric Con­struc­tion (PPVC), and lever­ag­ing 3D mod­el­ling soft­ware BIM (Build­ing In­for­ma­tion Model­ing).</p>
    <p>CCDC will pro­cure ser­vices from like-minded safety part­ners while strength­en­ing WSH own­er­ship among work­ers through in-house train­ing ses­sions and adopt­ing a WSH tech­nol­ogy ecosys­tem to deepen ca­pa­bil­ity build­ing.</p>
    <p>“We have plans to raise our WSH per­for­mance even fur­ther to be among the best,” Mr Kwek adds.</p>


